- Release Notes ------------------------------------------------------------- -

   The disk set consists of hi-definition concert footage and audio from their
   November 3rd, 2007 show at The Theater of Living Arts in Philadelphia,
   Pennsylvania. This DVD and audio CD features Saosin at their peak, live in
   Philadelphia on November 3rd 2007. The DVD features the entire set as well as
   music videos, and some extras, while the CD features five live tracks and
   three alternate versions of Saosin favorites. This is the DVD packaging.
